# Goal
geometry_msgs/PoseStamped site    # where to look (map frame, from the web map click)
float32 search_timeout            # seconds to search for a sock (0 = default)
---
# Result
bool success
string outcome                    # human-readable end state
---
# Feedback
string state                      # current FSM state (NAVIGATE/SEARCH/PICK/DEPOSIT/...)
